Both the abnormal bodies and many of the symptoms are associated with Parkinsons disease and Alzheimers the institute points out so scientists do not know whether the ailment is a distinct disease or a variant of Alzheimers or Parkinsons
Supporters of the measure say the decision could help find cures to diseases including cancer AIDS spinal cord injuries Parkinsons disease and Alzheimers disease more quickly than had been expected
The investigators identified two mutations in the same gene one associated with Parkinsons disease in the Basque families and the other which was linked to the disease in the English family
Although Parkinsons disease is usually not inherited the discovery of this gene and further study of how it works could open up new avenues of research for preventing or delaying the onset of the disease
